{"tid":209420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[this city is dying]好多職業都係一代不如一代","createTime":"2017-04-20T07:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T15:30:47.000Z","uid":83128,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4db64046cc00db59601be893835dc7bd2f426a2d","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"求其舉幾個例子<br />\n<br />\n已經唔洗講以前香港樓價，物價<br />\n<br />\n早出世既人真係好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcec45e47005ba488ea557a79f14fac5415edf9","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"屌未出哂<br />\n<br />\n求其舉幾個例子<br />\n<br />\n老師：教席難爭到仆街，又係contract又做到嘔，老屎忽perm位就爽yy<br />\n<br />\n社工：一筆過撥款之前，社工有幾好境，相信都唔洗我多講<br />\n<br />\n銀行：以前做銀行堪稱為「私營鐵飯碗」，而家？狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n公務員：福利差左好多，無pension，無40日假，雖然新制公務員依然屌打好多其他工<br />\n<br />\n諗到其他再講"},{"pid":"b3d51ab3d7c8ed50f6c01c7b68c57f75433e58cd","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"無人有同感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faea39bdae4dd6d70b9e110f62fe0faffc0a62dd","tid":209420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"IT?"},{"pid":"8f41d2ea30700a9e895e86a8635b4d4cc5477533","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"290fb7e3c644c2e1ff5d5f2c59f571a80d799682","tid":209420,"uid":235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36d1f68140bc25fc1640bea66b6fd4e59b7cc654","tid":209420,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:21:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你唔夠努力，唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"a0e0cf78debf3697cb8250817be1bdca131431b7","tid":209420,"uid":55929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:25:51.000Z","msg":"每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式"},{"pid":"e9c77bf630bbbec179ceddc0d613aa6f523c1d00","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你唔夠努力，唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n典型5，60後口吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c209646f77cc5bfb6a9d31c928c69c01b0174f","tid":209420,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你唔夠努力，唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n典型5，60後口吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀叔我食鹽多過你食米"},{"pid":"0b8b63d21e56e9d059548c76ffaa1819863d93c5","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式</blockquote><br />\n事實係 綜合番向上流動既機會、社會競爭、福利、工作前境、樓價、物價等等<br />\n<br />\n的確係一代不如一代"},{"pid":"1d026240617ca65f70f3215914816a62639265a7","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你唔夠努力，唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n典型5，60後口吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呀叔我食鹽多過你食米</blockquote><br />\n人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6f8d5e2a55d943ba0aee4df7cefec9e0a0c86e","tid":209420,"uid":55929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式</blockquote><br />\n事實係 綜合番向上流動既機會、社會競爭、福利、工作前境、樓價、物價等等<br />\n<br />\n的確係一代不如一代</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係以前打工係嗰一代嘅基層，到頭黎上左公屋，都係做返基層。姐基層嘅百分比冇咩點變。錯嘅只係話對生活水準嘅預期、幻想。<br />\n我反而覺得，真正嘅「進步空間」根本就越來越少，好多嘢都好似走到盡頭，冇得再新再強。<br />\n倒不如換個比較方式，比自己選擇返自己想得到嘅嘢。"},{"pid":"db364b6a841f89b2c725b695ba9ecd4bff0c4911","tid":209420,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式</blockquote><br />\n事實係 綜合番向上流動既機會、社會競爭、福利、工作前境、樓價、物價等等<br />\n<br />\n的確係一代不如一代</blockquote><br />\n個人能力都係<br />\n80年AL&gt;90年AL&gt;20年AL&gt;未代AL&gt;而加DSE"},{"pid":"ad7e046e67a39c0c065770f63b96a390920469a5","tid":209420,"uid":7846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0ebad11a007e7669faa58031e5bc64d1e758757","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行業選擇少..唔夠多元化<br />\n就算多都好..好多行業都待遇唔好, 政府社會唔多重視<br />\n年輕一代根本冇咩出頭嘅機會<br />\n政府仲話搞stem...淨講讀sci 都冇乜好嘅出路<br />\n唔通讀chem bio 出嚟做lab 咩..狗都唔屌啦</blockquote><br />\n香港就係咁，就係得金融地產呢啲<br />\n好多行業都underpay 例如傳媒貢獻咁大但人工就低過狗<br />\nbetween識幾個讀science既都去左做正苦工，無人做番lab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ca14df57539b4114bef81c5c6badbaa04c09cd","tid":209420,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"其實係資產價格過高啫.<br />\n<br />\n如果按番人均收入既升幅, 香港唔差過以前甚致更好.<br />\n分配問題, 唔係資源問題."},{"pid":"f30bdc455e8d3ea4724f99db25dc200687dc0c63","tid":209420,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f647c4cfc013a494496e5bc8be7ad722491c36","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式</blockquote><br />\n事實係 綜合番向上流動既機會、社會競爭、福利、工作前境、樓價、物價等等<br />\n<br />\n的確係一代不如一代</blockquote><br />\n個人能力都係<br />\n80年AL&gt;90年AL&gt;20年AL&gt;未代AL&gt;而加DSE</blockquote><br />\nDSE真係唔入流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前UE有A-Level果陣，難到嘔<br />\n利申：近末代AL"},{"pid":"58725bf8ff0a74aadacee683d8c91551dcc0bd38","tid":209420,"uid":11078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:35:26.000Z","msg":"香港行業只會越縮越少 香港無生產既地同本錢"},{"pid":"fe60d8c3c9c071f05f3a4ea69e8397d114a1aa96","tid":209420,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式</blockquote><br />\n事實係 綜合番向上流動既機會、社會競爭、福利、工作前境、樓價、物價等等<br />\n<br />\n的確係一代不如一代</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我意思係以前打工係嗰一代嘅基層，到頭黎上左公屋，都係做返基層。姐基層嘅百分比冇咩點變。錯嘅只係話對生活水準嘅預期、幻想。<br />\n我反而覺得，真正嘅「進步空間」根本就越來越少，好多嘢都好似走到盡頭，冇得再新再強。<br />\n倒不如換個比較方式，比自己選擇返自己想得到嘅嘢。</blockquote><br />\n科投發展太快<br />\n機械人遲下將會取代人力<br />\n覺得進步空間細因爲香港唔再係經濟起飛既時代，好多市場已飽和左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe29866702874b3ad5dc3a789290d80d7efc9800","tid":209420,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式</blockquote><br />\n事實係 綜合番向上流動既機會、社會競爭、福利、工作前境、樓價、物價等等<br />\n<br />\n的確係一代不如一代</blockquote><br />\n個人能力都係<br />\n80年AL&gt;90年AL&gt;20年AL&gt;未代AL&gt;而加DSE</blockquote><br />\nDSE真係唔入流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前UE有A-Level果陣，難到嘔<br />\n利申：近末代AL</blockquote>係<br />\n所以香港只會越來越倒退"},{"pid":"19b5ea2c05178eeca1c86ba59be047e6babbca17","tid":209420,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每代都有每代嘅難處，倒不如去轉個比較方式</blockquote><br />\n事實係 綜合番向上流動既機會、社會競爭、福利、工作前境、樓價、物價等等<br />\n<br />\n的確係一代不如一代</blockquote><br />\n個人能力都係<br />\n80年AL&gt;90年AL&gt;20年AL&gt;未代AL&gt;而加DSE</blockquote><br />\n愈嚟愈exam oriented<br />\n<br />\n課程內容無同大改進<br />\n離地離到識飛<br />\n<br />\n中學生學既唔係科目思考係背資料同寫番落對應既題目度"},{"pid":"764b1c8eccf2f9bae322eb4e0046f8bbea719306","tid":209420,"uid":58669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eva3Y3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feva3Y3.gif&h=1defb4bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20dd307cb3bdc395d550f5211f09f08442f2ff6f","tid":209420,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}